msgid "You can enable Split Touch Controls in the Controls settings."
msgstr "你可以在控制設置中啟用拆分觸控。"

msgid ""
"To place block, equip it in inventory and simply click on the spot where you "
"want to place it."
msgstr ""
"要放置方塊，將它裝備在手中中並點擊屏幕上其中一點即可。"

msgid "The [FF0000]Source of Life[-] only spawns at night."
msgstr "[FF0000]生命之源[-]僅在晚上生成。"

msgid ""
"The [00FF00]Boat[-] is good for travelling on more than [00FF00]Water[-]."
msgstr ""
"[00FF00]船[-]適用但不僅限於[00FF00]水[-]上行駛。"

msgid "Watch that rogue orchard! Growing trees can damage nearby buildings."
msgstr ""
"小心肆意生長的果園！樹木的生長會破壞附近的建築物。"

msgid "Plants can grow anywhere with the right type of soil."
msgstr "如有合適的土壤，植物可以在任何地方生長。"

msgid "Make some [00FF00]Torch[-] before you go exploring."
msgstr "探索之前，製作一些[00FF00]火把[-]。"

msgid "Complete [FF0000]Aarons'[-] quests to unlock the radar recipe."
msgstr "完成[FF0000]魔力師[-]的任務以解鎖雷達配方。"

msgid "Go into caves to easily find ore."
msgstr "洞穴中很容易找到礦石。"

msgid "Stronger enemies drop better items."
msgstr "強大的敵人掉落更好的物品。"

msgid "With the teleport staff you can teleport to any placed bed."
msgstr "使用傳送器，你可以傳送到任何地方。"

msgid ""
"If you die, you will be respawned near the last placed [00FF00]Bed[-] block."
msgstr ""
"如果你死了，你會在最後放置的[00FF00]床[-]的附近重生。"

msgid "A lost world resides deep underwater."
msgstr "深海里存在著一個迷失的世界。"

msgid   "Be sure to check out the official [FF0000]Discord[-]!"
msgstr  "別忘了加入官方[FF0000]Discord[-]服務器！"

msgid "Go to [FF0000]www.blockstory.net[-] for more info about the game."
msgstr ""
"到[FF0000] www.blockstory.net [-]去了解關於遊戲的更多資訊。"

msgid "Collect a spawner to take any creature with you."
msgstr ""
"收集生怪磚，就可以帶走任何生物。"

msgid "The amount of time you can fly is linked to your [FF0000]Mana[-]."
msgstr "你能飛行的時間與[FF0000]魔力值[-]有關。"

msgid "Creatures: Red - Aggressive, Yellow - Neutral, Green - peaceful."
msgstr ""
"生物: [FF0000]紅色 - 敵對[-]，[FFFF00]黃色 - 中立[-]，[00FF00]綠色 - 和平[-]。"

msgid ""
"Eliminate a spawner to prevent being overwhelmed by monsters (eg. spiders)."
msgstr ""
"拆掉生怪磚，以防止被怪物(如蜘蛛)淹沒。"

msgid "The [FF0000]Alchemist[-] is also a merchant."
msgstr "[FF0000]鍊金術士[-]也是一個商人。"

msgid ""
"DON'T stab an [FF0000]Electric Dragon[-] (or any other [FF0000]Dragon[-])!"
msgstr ""
"不要過早挑戰[FF0000]雷龍[-](或任何其他的[FF0000]龍[-])！"

msgid "Make a diving suit before traveling to [FF0000]Atlantis[-]."
msgstr "前往[FF0000]亞特蘭蒂斯[-]前要製造一件潛水服。"

msgid "[00FF00]Clouds[-] are pretty to look at, but will not hold you up."
msgstr "[00FF00]雲[-]相當好看，但並不能把你托住。"

msgid ""
"Hold a [00FF00]Bucket[-] of [00FF00]Water[-] in your hand to place water; "
"hold an empty [00FF00]Bucket[-] in your hand to collect [00FF00]Water[-]."
msgstr ""
"手持[00FF00]水桶[-]來放置水；手持空的[00FF00]桶[-]來收集[00FF00]水[-]。"

msgid ""
"Water in Forgotten Sky islands is often open to the sky below it - be "
"careful when swimming, you can fall out of the water into open air!"
msgstr ""
"被遺忘的天空中的島嶼裡的水域常常與下面的天空相連 - 游泳時要小心，你可能由水跌進天空中！"

msgid ""
"[00FF00]Iron Ore[-] glows a weak grey light - you may not be able to see it "
"when brighter ores are nearby."
msgstr ""
"[00FF00]鐵礦石[-]發出微弱的灰色光芒 - 當附近有更明亮的礦石時，你可能看不見它。"

msgid ""
"[00FF00]Sea Grass[-] contains trapped air. You can swim into it to replenish "
"your [FF0000]Breath[-] while deep underwater."
msgstr ""
"[00FF00]海草[-]中包含空氣。當在深水處的時候，你可以遊進它來補充你的[FF0000]氧氣值[-]。"

msgid "Sleeping restores your [FF0000]Mana[-] and [FF0000]Health[-]."
msgstr "通過睡眠恢復你的[FF0000]魔力值[-]和[FF0000]生命值[-]。"

msgid "Spend skill points on dig speed to dig faster."
msgstr ""
"花一些技能點在挖掘速度上以加快挖掘。"

msgid ""
"[00FF00]Lava[-], [00FF00]Acid[-], and [00FF00]Cactus[-] do damage when you "
"touch them."
msgstr ""
"當你觸摸[00FF00]熔岩[-]，[00FF00]硫酸[-]，[00FF00]仙人掌[-]和[FF00FF]蘑菇[-]時，你會受到傷害。"

msgid "Dig deep to find [FF0000]Moria[-] and the [FF0000]Underworld[-]."
msgstr "向下挖以去往[FF0000]地獄[-]。"

msgid "Fly high above to find a forgotten world."
msgstr "飛到高空去尋找被遺忘的世界。"

msgid "You can trade with [FF0000]The Alchemist[-] for useful items."
msgstr "你可以用有用的物件去和[FF0000]鍊金術士[-]交易。"

msgid "The recipe book can be found within the inventory window."
msgstr "配方書可以在揹包窗口內找到。"

msgid "Use skill points to make your character stronger."
msgstr ""
"花一些技能點去讓你的角色變得更強大"

msgid "Dont attack [FF0000]Ted[-]!!!"
msgstr "不要攻擊[FF0000]泰德[-]!!!"

msgid ""
"[FF0000]Quests[-] need to be completed for certain recipes to be unlocked."
msgstr ""
"需要完成[FF0000]任務[-]去解開某些配方。"

msgid ""
"Need [00FF00]Sulfur[-] or [00FF00]Unobtainium[-]? Go to the "
"[FF0000]Underworld[-]!"
msgstr ""
"需要[00FF00]硫磺[-]或[00FF00]難得素[-]？去[FF0000]地獄[-]找找！"

msgid "[00FF00]Sea Grass[-] can be used to make elevators."
msgstr "[00FF00]海草[-]可以用於製造簡易電梯。"

msgid "Trees you plant will not stop growing until they are full size."
msgstr ""
"你栽種的樹會一直生長直到完全長大。"

